summary:
Quantitative Risk Analyst within the Non-Retail Credit Risk Modelling department of ABN AMRO Bank N.V., a Dutch D-SIB. Active in the development of A-IRB credit risk models for Non-Retail portfolios.

Data scientist with proven analytic and mathematical ability through extensive academic research experience. Expert in sharing both applied and theoretical knowledge in varying contexts.
